    <dict>
      <key>anya_ai_intro</key>
      <string>Hello there. I am Anya, your little friend! You can chat and play with me. I love to talk about science, history, geography and anything else you are curious about. For example, you could say, “Hey Anya, tell me about the planets in our solar system.”  and I will tell you all about it. I can also tell you jokes, stories and riddles.  Just remember to say “Hey Anya” to get my attention.  We can also play with puppies, pop bubbles and do the hula hoop together. You can dress me up too! 
Oh! One more thing, if you want me to stop talking, just tickle me.</string>
      <key>anya_ai_hint2</key>
      <string>You can ask me to do things, such as “Hey Anya, Dance please”</string>
      <key>anya_ai_trouble_hearing</key>
      <string>Sorry, I had trouble hearing you. Could you repeat that please?</string>
      <key>anya_ai_hint3</key>
      <string>You can ask me to tell you a joke, riddle or a story by saying, “Hey Anya, tell me a story about a playful cat”</string>
      <key>anya_ai_hint1</key>
      <string>You can ask me to do things, such as  “Hey Anya, play with the puppy”</string>
